{"tid":1462950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［爭取外國支持］阻旅客回家=叫外國譴責示威者係暴徒","createTime":"2019-08-13T11:44:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T03:26:54.000Z","uid":186,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1e26eaf02e99cb5639f860dca7569fa320a122be","tid":1462950,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:44:55.000Z","msg":"你阻人返屋企<br />\n外國人搵大使館<br />\n外國要出聲話示威者係暴民<br />\n到時所有國家都話示威者暴民<br />\n咁贏d咩<br />\n自high圍爐？ 爭取全世界人話我地暴民<br />\n我唔講係唔係鬼。但兄弟究竟阻人走有咩行動目的，阻到旅客走就逼到外國支持香港？就達成到我地五大訴求？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你意見唔同，我唔會鬧你咩派別。呢啲叫不分化。<br />\n你做咩路線，我唔會強烈譴責你，話你係鬼。呢啲叫不割蓆。<br />\n你做咩唔岩，我唔會舉手報警。呢啲叫不篤灰。<br />\n<br />\n唔係政治潔癖，呢d叫係逼死自己。<br />\n連外國支持都放棄，靠咩贏？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n行動目標係爭取外國支持<br />\n唔係同旅客攬抄啊"},{"pid":"788e1c5b61011aea4ed08747917cde417eb0cd99","tid":1462950,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:45:32.000Z","msg":"難道想爭取外國人話我地係暴民 animals?"},{"pid":"8e0c1a6bdda256ab2d873059f50f21194565b2a5","tid":1462950,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:45:57.000Z","msg":"請各位手足諗一諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece891bdb09256a8bd99378b567b4cdb6000117c","tid":1462950,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:46:33.000Z","msg":"攬抄係同大陸攬炒<br />\n搞外國人 叫自焚啊"},{"pid":"e3644a67e9d77e40d6436e6a8f44452652c7e3b6","tid":1462950,"uid":81518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:46:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1807d8c1a3dccf3e42a85d9b6fb9d38f0f523907","tid":1462950,"uid":17741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:48:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c5c82ef4e16813291074bb2bbd001ba084ae7fbf","tid":1462950,"uid":108269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:48:55.000Z","msg":"滯留咗兩日仲會唔怪你先奇"},{"pid":"c9aaca8d29a0efd8e2d6696522b6b1dcfd2fe8